@obe1123
I see you have uploaded single episodes of the walking dead. Well its not that hard to upload full seasons. If you download the full season episode by episode or you have the season disc its pretty much the same. Once you have collected the full season save all episodes into a single folder example "The Walking Dead Season 3" use a program like winrar or winzip to compress the files. Then create a torrent like you would any other when the compression is done. Then upload like you would any other torrent but with a full season you need to seed longer so people don't get stuck on a % while downloading a bigger file.
